                    laudantium perferendis ipsum dolorem dolore mollitia laboriosam saepe
                    cum modi aperiam in, numquam esse nesciunt nulla possimus illo ducimus
                    neque. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Vel hic
                    incidunt modi, ad quidem tenetur alias deserunt quibusdam tempore iste
                    labore culpa libero ipsa in. Quod perspiciatis nisi totam eveniet.
                </p>
                <hr />
            </article> --}}
        </main>

        <footer class="w3-padding-16 w3-center">
            <i>Designed and coded by Claudia Yile, Min Maung and Noah Becker&nbsp;&nbsp;</i>&nbsp;&nbsp;&copy; <span class="this-yr"></span>
        </footer>

        <script src="/javascript/footer.js"></script>
    </body>
</html>
